    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Thou art__ the joy of__ the heav---en---ly__ or--ders__ found___ on___ high,__ and of us men____ up--on__ earth,___ a__ strong help and__ pro--tec--tion. Save____ us, O__ pure Vir-gin__ and__ Moth---er of__ God, as we flee___ un--to___ thee__ in___ faith; for af-ter God,__ we have set____ all__ our hope__ on___ thee,__ seek-ing ref-uge in thy__ might-----y____ strength."
